<div class = "row large-12 columns">
    <h1> <%=t('c_general.what_we_do.title')%></h1>
    <p> Civil society makes a unique contribution to the SUN movement. Here’s just some of the ways that we are supporting the fight against hunger and malnutrition: </p>
    <ul class='circles'>
      <li><b>Raising our voice</b> –  through social mobilisation, advocacy and campaigning we help to ensure that national development plans respond to the experiences of those affected by malnutrition. We work with communities to increase awareness of their right to food and nutrition. And we raise the profile of nutrition amongst decision makers and encourage governments accelerate progress. </li>
      <li><b>Building Capacity </b> – through our global network we identify and share examples of best practice in tackling malnutrition. By collecting and communicating the latest evidence we provide governments with solutions and by facilitating training to alliances we build the capacity of civil society as implementation partners.</li>
      <li><b>Monitoring Progress </b> - from a local to a global level we are tracking progress in eliminating malnutrition. We are monitoring nutrition spending, collecting data to ensure we leave no one behind and holding governments accountable to their promises.</li>
    </ul>
